snippet.title: Tartaros - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Tartaros is 3D first person  puzzle platformer set in greek underworld. Inspired by games such as Portal and PS1 games. 

STORY:
Help Persephone on her way up back to the World of living . On this journey you will meet with many mythical creatures and characters from ancient legends and stories.

Game link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3201100/Tartaros_Demo/
Our community discord: https://discord.gg/Fm9d3RkPne
